narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A requirement for the major. It was not a ton of work, but all the work done served an excellent purpose. I would recommend it.

Nice prep course for all senior ling majors going into their final semester. Be prepared ahead of time if Pinango teaches it again. Get an advisor quickly to help you work on your research project since Pinango's lectures and assignments will be of little help
